• Member of regular Dutch-German Marketing Steering Group, input related to intercultural marketing, media policy and management support; 
• Editing, translating, production of Dutch, German, English web content and marketing content for Try-act EWIV, members and associates, legal and business correspondence, quotes; 
• Staff- and marketing liaison, networking, wherever possible generating new contacts, projects and leads for Try-act EWIV, members and associates;
• Social media info concerning employment mobility and -flexibility via LinkedIn, XING, Twitter in Dutch, German, English (incidentally other languages) for Try-act EWIV;
• special focus on interculturality and national legal frameworks re development of employment mobility and -flexibility in the Netherlands, Germany, Europe; focus on generational change, integration, senior employees, gender parity, diversity; information re employment mobility in a national and European context; Corporate Governance.

AXXAZ Europe GmbH is a worldwide specialist in recruitment & selection / executive search, staffing & secondment, payrolling, payroll administration, project management. AXXAZ Europe GmbH specialises in Marine, Logistics, Hospitality, Medical, Metal & Industry and 50Plus staff.
• Editing, translating, production of Dutch, German, English web content and marketing content for AXXAZ Europe GmbH, legal and business correspondence, quotes;
• Staff- and marketing liaison, networking, wherever possible generating new contacts, projects and leads for AXXAZ Europe GmbH;
• Social media via LinkedIn, XING, Twitter in Dutch, German, English (incidentally other languages) for AXXAZ Europe GmbH.

• Editing, translating Dutch, German, English content for Quotion sales promotion and for sales staff qualification and training programmes; 
• Networking and - wherever possible - generating new contacts, projects and leads for Quotion in the Netherlands;
• Incidental textual support for social media presence on LinkedIn, Twitter in German, Dutch, English for Quotion.

AXXAZ Marine is a specialised division of AXXAZ Europe GmbH. AXXAZ Europe is a provider of bespoke staffing solutions for freight and passenger tranport, road transport, shipping, air and rail transport. AXXAZ Europe operates with local branch offices, joint ventures and strategic alliances in every state of the European Union.
• Editing, production of German, Dutch, English web content for AXXAZ Marine; 
• Translating legal and corporate texts for AXXAZ Marine;
• Social Media presence whenever approperiate on LinkedIn, XING, Twitter for AXXAZ Marine.

• Translating legal and commercial texts, correspondence, quotes, editing of German, English Dutch texts and content for PayLohn GmbH (legal successor of former DAXXA Deutschland GmbH - DAXXA Hospitality, DAXXA Medical & Nursing Staff, DAXXA Driver Team, DAXXA Greece, DAXXA Bulgaria, DAXXA Payrolling); 
